{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":481,"text":"We live in an incredibly busy world."},{"time":3073,"text":"The pace of life is often frantic,\nour minds are always busy,"},{"time":6594,"text":"and we're always doing something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":8795,"text":"So with that in mind,\nI'd like you just to take a moment"},{"time":11511,"text":"to think, when did you last take\nany time to do nothing?"},{"time":16819,"text":"Just 10 minutes, undisturbed?"},{"time":19348,"text":"And when I say nothing, I do mean nothing."},{"time":21625,"text":"So that's no emailing,\ntexting, no Internet,"},{"time":24245,"text":"no TV, no chatting, no eating, no reading."},{"time":28303,"text":"Not even sitting there\nreminiscing about the past"},{"time":30613,"text":"or planning for the future."},{"time":32754,"text":"Simply doing nothing."},{"time":36440,"text":"I see a lot of very blank faces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38023,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":39048,"text":"You probably have to go a long way back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40991,"text":"And this is an extraordinary thing, right?"},{"time":43023,"text":"We're talking about our mind."},{"time":45143,"text":"The mind, our most valuable\nand precious resource,"},{"time":48431,"text":"through which we experience\nevery single moment of our life."},{"time":52447,"text":"The mind that we rely upon"},{"time":54623,"text":"to be happy, content,\nemotionally stable as individuals,"},{"time":59121,"text":"and at the same time,\nto be kind and thoughtful"},{"time":61525,"text":"and considerate\nin our relationships with others."},{"time":65249,"text":"This is the same mind that we depend upon"},{"time":67361,"text":"to be focused, creative, spontaneous,"},{"time":70857,"text":"and to perform at our very best\nin everything that we do."},{"time":74912,"text":"And yet, we don't take\nany time out to look after it."},{"time":79013,"text":"In fact, we spend more time\nlooking after our cars,"},{"time":82050,"text":"our clothes and our hair than we --"},{"time":84057,"text":"okay, maybe not our hair,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85328,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86353,"text":"but you see where I'm going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88127,"text":"The result, of course,\nis that we get stressed."},{"time":90814,"text":"You know, the mind whizzes away\nlike a washing machine"},{"time":93563,"text":"going round and round,\nlots of difficult, confusing emotions,"},{"time":96979,"text":"and we don't really know\nhow to deal with that."},{"time":102312,"text":"And the sad fact\nis that we are so distracted"},{"time":105804,"text":"that we're no longer present\nin the world in which we live."},{"time":110359,"text":"We miss out on the things\nthat are most important to us,"},{"time":113691,"text":"and the crazy thing\nis that everybody just assumes,"},{"time":116122,"text":"that's the way life is, so we've just\nkind of got to get on with it."},{"time":119485,"text":"That's really not how it has to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121719,"text":"So I was about 11 when I went along\nto my first meditation class."},{"time":126159,"text":"And trust me, it had all the stereotypes\nthat you can imagine,"},{"time":129383,"text":"the sitting cross-legged on the floor,"},{"time":131778,"text":"the incense, the herbal tea,\nthe vegetarians, the whole deal,"},{"time":135177,"text":"but my mom was going and I was intrigued,\nso I went along with her."},{"time":138970,"text":"I'd also seen a few kung fu movies,"},{"time":140975,"text":"and secretly I kind of thought\nI might be able to learn how to fly,"},{"time":144345,"text":"but I was very young at the time."},{"time":147059,"text":"Now as I was there, I guess,\nlike a lot of people,"},{"time":150170,"text":"I assumed that it was just\nan aspirin for the mind."},{"time":153834,"text":"You get stressed, you do some meditation."},{"time":155811,"text":"I hadn't really thought that it could be\nsort of preventative in nature,"},{"time":159656,"text":"until I was about 20, when a number\nof things happened in my life"},{"time":163315,"text":"in quite quick succession,"},{"time":165749,"text":"really serious things\nwhich just flipped my life upside down"},{"time":169216,"text":"and all of a sudden\nI was inundated with thoughts,"},{"time":172138,"text":"inundated with difficult emotions\nthat I didn't know how to cope with."},{"time":175719,"text":"Every time I sort of pushed one down,"},{"time":177759,"text":"another one would pop back up again."},{"time":179584,"text":"It was a really very stressful time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181820,"text":"I guess we all deal with stress\nin different ways."},{"time":186138,"text":"Some people will bury themselves in work,\ngrateful for the distraction."},{"time":190748,"text":"Others will turn to their friends,\ntheir family, looking for support."},{"time":194058,"text":"Some people hit the bottle,\nstart taking medication."},{"time":197952,"text":"My own way of dealing with it\nwas to become a monk."},{"time":201020,"text":"So I quit my degree,\nI headed off to the Himalayas,"},{"time":204657,"text":"I became a monk, and I started\nstudying meditation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208173,"text":"People often ask me\nwhat I learned from that time."},{"time":212234,"text":"Well, obviously it changed things."},{"time":214470,"text":"Let's face it, becoming a celibate monk\nis going to change a number of things."},{"time":218484,"text":"But it was more than that."},{"time":221064,"text":"It taught me -- it gave me\na greater appreciation,"},{"time":224403,"text":"an understanding for the present moment."},{"time":228062,"text":"By that I mean not being lost in thought,"},{"time":232022,"text":"not being distracted,"},{"time":233858,"text":"not being overwhelmed\nby difficult emotions,"},{"time":237673,"text":"but instead learning how to be\nin the here and now,"},{"time":241226,"text":"how to be mindful, how to be present."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244160,"text":"I think the present moment\nis so underrated."},{"time":247625,"text":"It sounds so ordinary,"},{"time":249412,"text":"and yet we spend so little time\nin the present moment"},{"time":253131,"text":"that it's anything but ordinary."},{"time":255496,"text":"There was a research paper that came\nout of Harvard, just recently,"},{"time":259305,"text":"that said on average, our minds\nare lost in thought"},{"time":262095,"text":"almost 47 percent of the time."},{"time":265080,"text":"47 percent."},{"time":267127,"text":"At the same time, this sort\nof constant mind-wandering"},{"time":270000,"text":"is also a direct cause of unhappiness."},{"time":272659,"text":"Now we're not here for that long anyway,"},{"time":277727,"text":"but to spend almost half\nof our life lost in thought"},{"time":281953,"text":"and potentially quite unhappy,"},{"time":283959,"text":"I don't know, it just kind\nof seems tragic, actually,"},{"time":286656,"text":"especially when there's something\nwe can do about it,"},{"time":289613,"text":"when there's a positive,\npractical, achievable,"},{"time":293261,"text":"scientifically proven technique"},{"time":296245,"text":"which allows our mind to be more healthy,"},{"time":298471,"text":"to be more mindful and less distracted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302619,"text":"And the beauty of it is that even though"},{"time":305038,"text":"it need only take about 10 minutes a day,"},{"time":307437,"text":"it impacts our entire life."},{"time":311195,"text":"But we need to know how to do it."},{"time":312915,"text":"We need an exercise."},{"time":314175,"text":"We need a framework\nto learn how to be more mindful."},{"time":317317,"text":"That's essentially what meditation is."},{"time":319240,"text":"It's familiarizing ourselves\nwith the present moment."},{"time":321755,"text":"But we also need to know\nhow to approach it in the right way"},{"time":324810,"text":"to get the best from it."},{"time":326691,"text":"And that's what these are for,\nin case you've been wondering,"},{"time":329661,"text":"because most people assume"},{"time":331922,"text":"that meditation\nis all about stopping thoughts,"},{"time":334677,"text":"getting rid of emotions,\nsomehow controlling the mind,"},{"time":337738,"text":"but actually it's quite\ndifferent from that."},{"time":340338,"text":"It's more about stepping back,"},{"time":342723,"text":"sort of seeing the thought clearly,"},{"time":345083,"text":"witnessing it coming and going,\nemotions coming and going"},{"time":347822,"text":"without judgment,\nbut with a relaxed, focused mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353462,"text":"So for example, right now,"},{"time":355597,"text":"if I focus too much on the balls,"},{"time":358058,"text":"then there's no way I can relax\nand talk to you at the same time."},{"time":361209,"text":"Equally, if I relax too much\ntalking to you,"},{"time":363337,"text":"there's no way I can focus on the balls."},{"time":365267,"text":"I'm going to drop them."},{"time":366473,"text":"Now in life, and in meditation,"},{"time":369115,"text":"there'll be times when the focus\nbecomes a little bit too intense,"},{"time":372535,"text":"and life starts to feel a bit like this."},{"time":376542,"text":"It's a very uncomfortable\nway to live life,"},{"time":378703,"text":"when you get this tight and stressed."},{"time":380819,"text":"At other times, we might take our foot off\nthe gas a little bit too much,"},{"time":384324,"text":"and things just become a sort\nof little bit like this."},{"time":386920,"text":"Of course in meditation --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":388609,"text":"(Snores)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":389634,"text":"we're going to end up falling asleep."},{"time":391443,"text":"So we're looking for a balance,\na focused relaxation"},{"time":394169,"text":"where we can allow thoughts to come and go"},{"time":397205,"text":"without all the usual involvement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399938,"text":"Now, what usually happens\nwhen we're learning to be mindful"},{"time":403236,"text":"is that we get distracted by a thought."},{"time":406180,"text":"Let's say this is an anxious thought."},{"time":407976,"text":"Everything's going fine,\nand we see the anxious thought."},{"time":410626,"text":"\"Oh, I didn't realize\nI was worried about that.\""},{"time":413173,"text":"You go back to it, repeat it."},{"time":414649,"text":"\"Oh, I am worried."},{"time":415836,"text":"I really am worried.\nWow, there's so much anxiety.\""},{"time":418295,"text":"And before we know it, right,"},{"time":420079,"text":"we're anxious about feeling anxious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423041,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":424073,"text":"You know, this is crazy."},{"time":425414,"text":"We do this all the time,\neven on an everyday level."},{"time":428577,"text":"If you think about the last time\nyou had a wobbly tooth."},{"time":433880,"text":"You know it's wobbly,\nand you know that it hurts."},{"time":437200,"text":"But what do you do every 20, 30 seconds?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440737,"text":"(Mumbling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442642,"text":"It does hurt."},{"time":443835,"text":"And we reinforce the storyline, right?"},{"time":446404,"text":"And we just keep telling ourselves,\nand we do it all the time."},{"time":449385,"text":"And it's only in learning\nto watch the mind in this way"},{"time":452097,"text":"that we can start to let go\nof those storylines and patterns of mind."},{"time":456529,"text":"But when you sit down\nand you watch the mind in this way,"},{"time":459230,"text":"you might see many different patterns."},{"time":461109,"text":"You might find a mind\nthat's really restless and --"},{"time":463766,"text":"the whole time."},{"time":465607,"text":"Don't be surprised if you feel\na bit agitated in your body"},{"time":468781,"text":"when you sit down to do nothing\nand your mind feels like that."},{"time":472542,"text":"You might find a mind that's very dull"},{"time":474942,"text":"and boring, and it's just,\nalmost mechanical,"},{"time":477278,"text":"it just seems it's as if you're\ngetting up, going to work,"},{"time":480481,"text":"eat, sleep, get up, work."},{"time":482962,"text":"Or it might just be\nthat one little nagging thought"},{"time":485486,"text":"that just goes round and round your mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":490640,"text":"Well, whatever it is,"},{"time":492006,"text":"meditation offers the opportunity,\nthe potential to step back"},{"time":497645,"text":"and to get a different perspective,"},{"time":500183,"text":"to see that things aren't always\nas they appear."},{"time":505055,"text":"We can't change every little thing\nthat happens to us in life,"},{"time":510793,"text":"but we can change\nthe way that we experience it."},{"time":514224,"text":"That's the potential\nof meditation, of mindfulness."},{"time":517961,"text":"You don't have to burn any incense,"},{"time":520535,"text":"and you definitely don't have\nto sit on the floor."},{"time":522940,"text":"All you need to do\nis to take 10 minutes out a day"},{"time":526853,"text":"to step back, to familiarize yourself\nwith the present moment"},{"time":530390,"text":"so that you get to experience\na greater sense"},{"time":533076,"text":"of focus, calm and clarity in your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537487,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538709,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}